Actor Johnny Depp talks with Charlie 
Rose about the film "The Lone Ranger" and his career.  In "The Lone Ranger," Depp plays Tonto, the title 
character's Native American sidekick. (" Charlie Rose " airs 
weeknights on PBS and Bloomberg Television. Source: Charlie 
Rose)  Running Time: 29:12
 